text: This place is a hidden gem. $1 for mutton stick, cheap and nice tasting mala. 2nd time eating here and the taste is consistant. Deserve a 5* for the taste and price.
The portions are very generous for the price and the taste is also very good.
Value for money Mala store. Delicious mala hotpot. For dishes, the grilled fish, spinach is recommended. Tomato with egg is too sweet
